<p>Are you sure you want to remove this book from your library? You won't be able to retrieve notes for that book anymore.</p>
<div class="panel panel-default">
    <p class="panel-body">{{book.title}}</p>
</div>
<form method="post" action="/book/{{book.id}}/remove">
    <button class="btn btn-danger" type="submit">Confirm Removal</button>
</form>